<li>Koppelmann, U.: <i>Produktmarketing</i> 6. Auflage, Berlin 2000, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3540671471" class="internal">ISBN 3-540-67147-1</a></li>
<li>Koppelmann, U.; Spies, H.: <i>Integrated Design Management.</i> Fördergesellschaft Produktmarketing, Cologne 1993, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3922292283" class="internal">ISBN 3-922292-28-3</a></li>
<li>Meyer, D.: <i>Design management in middlesized companies</i>, German Design Management Institute, Hagen und German Design Council, Frankfurt a. M. 1994, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3922885713" class="internal">ISBN 3-922885-71-3</a></li>
<li>Mozota, B.: <i>Design management: using design to built brand value and corporate innovation.</i> Allworth Press, New York 2003, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1581152833" class="internal">ISBN 1-58115-283-3</a></li>
<li>Myerson, J.: <i>IDEO: Masters of Innovation</i>, Neues Publishing Company, 2001, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3823854852" class="internal">ISBN 3-8238-5485-2</a></li>
<li>Oakley, M.: <i>Managing Product Design</i>, London 1984, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/047181637X" class="internal">ISBN 0-471-81637-X</a></li>
